(1146, 180, 'item_0_content', 'Mr. Fishman serves as the firm’s Managing Partner. He has experience in both the fields of real estate litigation and bankruptcy. Mr. Fishman also has extensive experience in all phases of real estate law, including title resolution and VA, FHA and conventional foreclosures. He has lectured in the fields of foreclosure and bankruptcy law, and has considerable experience in the area of single family and commercial real estate transactions. In addition to his various Bar admissions, Mr. Fishman is a member of the Mortgage Bankers Association of America, the Mortgage Bankers Association of Florida, the Florida Real Estate Brokers, and the Bankruptcy Bar Association of the Southern District of Florida. Mr. Fishman is listed in the Who’s Who in American Law.'),
