(1205, 182, 'content', 'Shapiro, Fishman &amp; Gaché, LLP has over 35 years of experience in the mortgage industry, handling cases throughout the entire state of Florida.  Our primary focus is providing prompt and professional legal representation in the areas of creditors’ rights, foreclosure, bankruptcy, evictions and general commercial litigation.\r\n\r\nSFG provides quality legal services to institutional lenders, loan servicers and its other business clients.  The firm is committed to a high standard of performance while maintaining a consistently reliable work product.  We strive to be responsive to our clients’ needs and overall satisfaction with the firm.\r\n\r\nThe firm’s partners and associate attorneys have extensive experience in the industry, with the firm’s Managing Litigation Partner being Board Certified by the Florida Bar in the area of Business Litigation.  The firm maintains an extensive training program for its associate attorneys and staff so each can handle all facets of foreclosure, bankruptcy and eviction law.'),
